# LearnHub API Project Overview

LearnHub is an online training solution developed by Baishu Technology. The API is built with Java + Spring Boot 3, using a modular approach.

## Project Structure
- [learnhub-api](mdc:learnhub-api) - Java backend API project
- [learnhub-admin](mdc:learnhub-admin) - Admin frontend
- [learnhub-pc](mdc:learnhub-pc) - PC web interface
- [learnhub-h5](mdc:learnhub-h5) - Mobile web interface

## API Key Modules
- [learnhub-api/LearnHubApiApplication.java](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/LearnHubApiApplication.java) - Main application entry point
- [learnhub-api](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api) - API module containing controllers and API-specific logic
- [learnhub-common](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-common) - Common utilities and shared code
- [learnhub-resource](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-resource) - Resource management module
- [learnhub-course](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-course) - Course-related functionality
- [learnhub-system](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-system) - System management functionality

## Backend vs Frontend Controllers
- [Backend Controllers](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/backend) - Admin-facing API endpoints
- [Frontend Controllers](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/frontend) - Student-facing API endpoints

## Development and Deployment
- [pom.xml](mdc:learnhub-api/pom.xml) - Main Maven configuration file
- [Dockerfile](mdc:learnhub-api/Dockerfile) - Docker build configuration
- [compose.yml](mdc:compose.yml) - Docker Compose configuration
